headline.main: 99 Italians Surrender Without a Struggle To 2 British Medical Orderlies in Tunisia

lead_paragraph: WITH THE BRITISH FORCES, in Northern Tunisia, March 31 (Delayed) -- Two British medical orderlies captured ninety-eight Italian enlisted men and a major today without firing a shot.
abstract: 99 Itals surrender without struggle to 2 Brit med orderlies, Tunis
